Fresh Pi session: PR DRAFTING ONLY.

Inputs:
- User prompt: {{run.dir}}/prompt/prompt.md
- Design: {{run.dir}}/design/design.md
- Execution summaries, regression reports, and review reports: {{run.dir}}
- Worktree: {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Draft clear pull request metadata for the accepted change.

Rules:
- Do not edit source code, call GitHub, or push.
- Summarize the change, validation performed, and notable risks.
- Fail only if accurate PR metadata cannot yet be produced; a failed draft is retried.

Write:
- Title: {{run.dir}}/pr/pr-title.txt
- Body: {{run.dir}}/pr/pr-body.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/pr/draft-status.json

Status:
{"status":"pass","summary":"PR metadata drafted","issues_file":null}

The body should include Summary, Implementation notes, Validation, and Risks or follow-up.
